c: 9
v: 94
t: "Babarusilinjia ebichila nimwakhakalukha khubo. boola; “Mularera ebichila tawe shikhulabasuubila tawe, toto Nyasaye akhuboolele amakhuwa kenyu, ne alalola amakhuwa kenyu nende Omurumwa wuwe, mana mulikalusibwa khumumanyi wakefisile nende akabulafu, naye alibaboolela kalia akamwakholanga"